OL,3,CMajor Stockport roundabout reopens
OL,4,Cafter year-long closure
OL,6,FA major roundabout in the centre of
OL,7,FStockport has re-opened after a year
OL,8,Flong overhaul to reconstruct the
OL,9,Frailway line below it.
OL,11,FThe Greek Street roundabout in
OL,12,FStockport is a key thoroughfare
OL,13,Fthrough the town and sits above the
OL,14,FWest Coast mainline.
OL,16,FNetwork Rail invested #20 million
OL,17,Freplacing Greek Street bridge to
OL,18,Fsecure both the road above and railway
OL,19,Fbelow for the next 120 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
