OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774714287
OL,3,CMajor Stockport roundabout reopens
OL,4,Cafter year-long closure
OL,6,FIn August the former 67-year-old
OL,7,Fstructure was removed and replaced
OL,8,Fwith a new bridge comprised of 51
OL,9,Fstructural elements ` all lifted in by
OL,10,Fcrane during a 21-day railway closure.
OL,12,FSince then work to reinstate the
OL,13,Fcarriageway, buried utilities like
OL,14,Fdrainage, power cables and gas and
OL,15,Fwater mains has taken place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
