PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774714287
OL,3,CMajor Stockport roundabout reopens
OL,4,Cafter year-long closure
OL,6,FPatrick Vallely from Network Rail
OL,7,Fsaid: "Replacing Greek Street bridge
OL,8,Fwas a massive feat of civil
OL,9,Fengineering which has impacted people
OL,10,Fright across Stockport for over a
OL,11,Fyear, so I'd like to say a huge thank
OL,12,Fyou to everyone for bearing with us.
OL,13,FThis essential project now secures the
OL,14,Ffuture of this structure and will
OL,15,Fprovide a safe and reliable road and
OL,16,Frailway network for decades to come."
OL,26,@oD@GOUxD@eO]
